  - Admin: red badge with shield icon
  - Manager: blue badge with person icon
  - Lines added: ~5 lines (part of welcome section)

**Usage Pattern:**
```javascript
// Single role
router.use('/admin/users', requireAdmin);

// Multiple roles
router.use('/admin/movies', requireRole(['admin', 'manager']));
```

**Existing Support:**
- User model already had `role` enum: ['admin', 'manager']
- No database changes required

